OL,3,CStoke City to build new multi-million
OL,4,Cpound training ground
OL,6,FITV News Central's sport correspondent
OL,7,FDan Salisbury-Jones reports.
OL,9,Fplayers will have "no excuses" after
OL,10,Fthe biggest financial investment since
OL,11,Fthe club built its stadium in the
OL,12,F1990s, according to its director.
OL,14,FToday plans were announced for a #10-
OL,15,F12m training ground development - with
OL,16,Fmore space for the first team, academy
OL,17,Fand women.
