OL,3,CStoke City to build new multi-million
OL,4,Cpound training ground
OL,6,FAt the current training facility,
OL,7,Fwhich was only built 15 years ago,
OL,8,FVice-Chairman Richard Smith told me
OL,9,Fhis vision.
OL,11,FHe said: "Especially with the growth
OL,12,Fof women's football, we felt that it
OL,13,Fwas time that we perhaps looked at
OL,14,Fbuilding something new and the
OL,15,Fsolution that we came up with was that
OL,16,Fwe would build a new facility for our
OL,17,Ffirst team.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
