OL,3,CStoke City to build new multi-million
OL,4,Cpound training ground
OL,6,F"We're investing about #10 million and
OL,7,Fthen, when we'd completed that, we're
OL,8,Fgoing to refurbish the building that
OL,9,Fwe're sitting in now. So that will be
OL,10,Ffor the academy and the women's team
OL,11,Fgoing forward."
OL,13,FHe also explained why it makes sense
OL,14,Ffor the club to invest in this way,
OL,15,Frather than splashing out on a new
OL,16,Fstriker.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
