OL,3,CStoke City to build new multi-million
OL,4,Cpound training ground
OL,6,F"Well, it's an interesting question.
OL,7,FWhen we're working with the profit and
OL,8,Fsustainability rules that we're all
OL,9,Fgoverned by in the EFL, when we are
OL,10,Finvesting in our infrastructure, it
OL,11,Fdoesn't count in the same way towards
OL,12,Fhow you're judged in terms of your
OL,13,Fprofitability. Whereas if you invest
OL,14,Fin the team, it counts straightaway."
