OL,3,CStoke City to build new multi-million
OL,4,Cpound training ground
OL,6,FStoke City Sporting Director Jon
OL,7,FWalters told me: "To have a new #12
OL,8,Fmillion building, state of the art, on
OL,9,Fsite is phenomenal. It's a huge draw
OL,10,Ffor players, staff members alike...
OL,11,Fthere's no excuses whatsoever. You
OL,12,Fhave the best facility around."
OL,14,FThe building will be ready in
OL,15,FSeptember 2025 - they will hope to
OL,16,Fhave a Premier League squad using it.
